thread.title: Freed Saudi prince faces lingering questions

title: Freed Saudi prince faces lingering questions
text:
Freed Saudi prince faces lingering questions Monday, January 29, 2018 - 02:04 
Financial sources say banks are keeping their distance from Saudi Arabian Prince Alwaleed bin Talal, after the sudden release of the investor and other members of the country's elite from a corruption probe left many unanswered questions surrounding the purge.
